    "content": "RUN_SEED=530809af-e36f-4daf-ad57-1764ebb78a24\nNATIVE_GAUNTLET EASY T7_REPEAT_EASY_20260525_016\n\nMaya, this is T7 repetition run 016 for the easy T6 task class in:\n/Users/gaganarora/Desktop/my projects/active_graph/activegraph\n\nPurpose: measure whether the T6 easy capability repeats on a fresh target.\n\nDo not reuse these prior easy targets:\n- activegraph.core.graph.Graph.store\n- activegraph.runtime.patterns.PatternMatcher.matches\n- activegraph.tools.cache.ToolCache.from_events\n- activegraph.packs.PackPrompt.from_body\n- activegraph.core.event.Event.to_dict\n- activegraph.behaviors.base.RelationBehavior.run\n- activegraph.core.clock.Clock.now\n- activegraph.core.ids.IDGen.object\n- activegraph.core.ids.IDGen.event\n- activegraph.core.clock.FrozenClock.now\n- activegraph.core.clock.TickingClock.now\n- activegraph.core.ids.IDGen.relation\n- activegraph.core.graph.Object.to_dict\n- activegraph.core.graph.Relation.to_dict\n- activegraph.core.ids.IDGen.patch\n\nWorktree discipline:\n- Work in /Users/gaganarora/Desktop/my projects/active_graph/activegraph.\n- There may be unrelated operator changes in this repo. Do not revert, delete, or rewrite unrelated files.\n- Commit only the file you intentionally change for this run.\n\nTask:\n1. cd into activegraph/. Confirm pwd and `git rev-parse --short HEAD`.\n2. Run the full pytest suite and capture the baseline summary line:\n     uv run pytest -q --tb=no > /tmp/t7-repeat-easy-016-pytest-before.out 2>&1; echo \"exit=$?\"; tail -3 /tmp/t7-repeat-easy-016-pytest-before.out\n   Record `pytest_before` as the integer count of passing tests.\n3. Pick ONE public function in activegraph/activegraph/ (not in tests/, not private with leading underscore) that has BOTH:\n     (a) no docstring, and\n     (b) at least one parameter OR the return value missing a type hint.\n4. Add a docstring matching activegraph/CONTRACT.md's documented format (Args / Returns / Raises sections as applicable) AND complete all missing annotations on that function. Do not change runtime behavior.\n5. Re-run pytest. `pytest_after` MUST be greater than or equal to `pytest_before`.\n6. Run `uv run ruff check <target_file>` for the file you changed; it must exit 0.\n7. Commit the target-file change in the activegraph inner repo. Commit message:\n     T7 easy 016: document and type <target_symbol>\n   Record the full commit SHA as `agent_commit_sha`.\n8. Create frames/t7-repeat-easy-016-20260525.proof with EXACTLY these keys, in this order:\n     hash=T7_REPEAT_EASY_20260525_016\n     run_seed=530809af-e36f-4daf-ad57-1764ebb78a24\n     pwd=<pwd output>\n     head=<git short head after commit>\n     target_file=<relative path>:<line number>\n     target_symbol=<fully.qualified.name>\n     agent_commit_sha=<full sha that committed the target_file change>\n     pytest_before=<int>\n     pytest_after=<int>\n     ruff_target_exit=0\n     verdict=native_easy_done\n9. Reply exactly:\n   MAYA_NATIVE_GAUNTLET_ACK T7_REPEAT_EASY_20260525_016 EASY frames/t7-repeat-easy-016-20260525.proof\n",
